** (MSG) (60A).....2.........3.........4.........5.........6
FROM_DATE IS INCORRECT !                                      1
TO_DATE IS INCORRECT !                                        2
FROM_DATE > TO_DATE !                                         3
NO DATA FOUND !                                               4
NO VALID DATA!                                                5
ENTER FROM_DATE !                                             6
ENTER TO_DATE !                                               7
X:DISPLAY EDI RAW DATA                                        8
EDI RAW DATA NOT FOUND!                                       9
F7:DOWNLOAD EDI RAW DATA                                     10
